page.title: 17West End Shop,Ingleton
page.content: {The West End Shop}is a grocers/Post Office owned by Mr.and Mrs. Whitehead. It sells all kinds of commodities:- { Sweets Pet Food { Drinks Tinned Food { Crisps Biscuits { Fresh Bread Baby Goods { Cakes Jams { Fruit and Vegetables Tights { Washing Powder Flour { Frozen Food Butter { }Fresh bread and cakes are delivered each morning to the shop and daily papers are on sale . Mr.Whitehead also delivers fresh milk to the villagers at 4 o'clock in the morning. Letters are collected from the post box at:- {11-00 hrs { 16-00 hrs { {
